<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA48">
<l>nīyaṉṟē nīrēṟ ṟulaka maṭiyaḷantāy</l>
<l>nīyaṉṟē niṉṟu niraimēyttāy – nīyaṉṟē</l>
<l>māvā yurampiḷantu māmaruti ṉūṭupōyt</l>
<l>tēvā curamporutāy ceṟṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You, isn’t it, received water [and] measured the world with [your] foot?</l>
<l>You, isn’t it, stood [and] grazed the herds? You, isn’t it,</l>
<l>tore apart the horse’s mouth, went in between the big myrobalan trees</l>
<l>[and] fought furiously [in the battle of] gods [and] Asuras.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
